WEBVTT

00:01:22.120 --> 00:01:22.520
Hey.

00:01:23.480 --> 00:01:24.520
What is this?

00:01:27.000 --> 00:01:27.460
This...

00:01:46.520 --> 00:01:48.200
The dead person is not Liu Jiang.

00:01:48.200 --> 00:01:49.320
To be exact,

00:01:49.440 --> 00:01:50.120
this person

00:01:50.120 --> 00:01:51.200
was not murdered.

00:01:51.360 --> 00:01:52.560
The autopsy revealed

00:01:52.840 --> 00:01:53.560
that there were

00:01:53.560 --> 00:01:55.400
multiple irregular masses in his body.

00:01:55.400 --> 00:01:56.880
The cut surface was grayish-white,

00:01:56.880 --> 00:01:58.000
brittle and hard in texture,

00:01:58.000 --> 00:01:59.920
with unclear boundaries from the surrounding tissue,

00:01:59.920 --> 00:02:02.320
which is consistent with the morphology of a primary malignant tumor.

00:02:02.320 --> 00:02:02.800
He died

00:02:02.840 --> 00:02:03.680
of cancer.

00:02:04.520 --> 00:02:05.250
Captain Sun,

00:02:05.360 --> 00:02:06.000
did Liu Jiang

00:02:06.000 --> 00:02:06.880
have cancer?

00:02:07.680 --> 00:02:08.479
Probably not.

00:02:09.440 --> 00:02:11.039
Even if he did,

00:02:12.120 --> 00:02:13.160
he couldn't have died so quickly.

00:02:13.160 --> 00:02:13.720
Moreover,

00:02:13.720 --> 00:02:16.480
in the remaining skin folds after burning,

00:02:16.480 --> 00:02:17.680
there are dark green,

00:02:17.680 --> 00:02:19.000
branch-like patterns.

00:02:19.000 --> 00:02:22.440
The bones also showed longitudinal splitting due to dehydration after burning.

00:02:22.440 --> 00:02:23.760
All these prove

00:02:23.960 --> 00:02:25.160
that his time of death

00:02:25.160 --> 00:02:27.560
was thirty-six hours before he was burned.

00:02:28.720 --> 00:02:29.920
If it's not Liu Jiang,

00:02:31.400 --> 00:02:32.200
then who is he?

00:02:38.240 --> 00:02:38.640
Hello?

00:02:41.200 --> 00:02:41.640
Okay.

00:02:45.800 --> 00:02:46.930
At Xifeng Mountain,

00:02:47.000 --> 00:02:48.660
another case was discovered.

00:02:52.160 --> 00:02:53.560
Found while walking the dog.

00:02:53.560 --> 00:02:55.560
The body parts weren't buried deep,

00:02:55.760 --> 00:02:57.290
so the dog dug them right up.

00:02:57.920 --> 00:02:59.440
The person who found the body said

00:02:59.440 --> 00:02:59.960
this area

00:02:59.960 --> 00:03:01.120
was closed off recently

00:03:01.120 --> 00:03:02.120
and just reopened.

00:03:02.120 --> 00:03:03.760
The killer probably didn't know it reopened

00:03:03.760 --> 00:03:05.160
and dumped the body here.

00:03:05.680 --> 00:03:07.540
He probably doesn't live nearby.

00:03:12.320 --> 00:03:12.800
Li Zhen,

00:03:12.880 --> 00:03:14.140
what's the situation?

00:03:14.440 --> 00:03:16.170
Here's the current situation.

00:03:16.640 --> 00:03:18.500
Judging from the decomposition,

00:03:18.760 --> 00:03:20.640
the victim has been dead for at least ten days.

00:03:20.640 --> 00:03:21.960
The body parts found so far,

00:03:21.960 --> 00:03:23.480
two legs and two arms,

00:03:23.880 --> 00:03:25.610
were all severed at the joints.

00:03:25.640 --> 00:03:26.700
The cuts are clean.

00:03:26.880 --> 00:03:28.940
But the decomposition is too severe.

00:03:29.160 --> 00:03:30.120
For specifics,

00:03:30.160 --> 00:03:31.890
we need to do a further autopsy.

00:03:32.200 --> 00:03:32.760
Zhen.

00:03:33.680 --> 00:03:35.680
These two both seem to be right arms.

00:03:41.600 --> 00:03:42.329
Brother Yan.

00:03:43.840 --> 00:03:45.500
Where should we investigate?

00:03:48.560 --> 00:03:49.560
What do you think?

00:03:50.640 --> 00:03:51.400
I think...

00:03:53.520 --> 00:03:55.600
I think if this person died of cancer,

00:03:56.079 --> 00:03:57.120
the hospital must have records.

00:03:57.120 --> 00:03:59.050
It's also possible he died at home.

00:04:00.120 --> 00:04:00.720
Then,

00:04:00.840 --> 00:04:01.720
the village committee,

00:04:01.720 --> 00:04:02.400
sub-district office,

00:04:02.400 --> 00:04:03.200
or police station

00:04:03.200 --> 00:04:04.680
must have issued a death certificate.

00:04:04.680 --> 00:04:05.280
Moreover,

00:04:05.360 --> 00:04:06.120
based on his

00:04:06.320 --> 00:04:07.160
time of death,

00:04:07.160 --> 00:04:07.800
cause of death,

00:04:07.800 --> 00:04:08.520
and age,

