00:04:10.640 --> 00:04:12.400
Then how did he end up

00:04:12.400 --> 00:04:14.200
burned in Liu Jiang's hometown?

00:04:14.560 --> 00:04:15.160
Also,

00:04:15.720 --> 00:04:16.779
