00:04:28.440 --> 00:04:29.500
When they arrived,

00:04:29.720 --> 00:04:31.380
the fire had already started,

00:04:31.640 --> 00:04:32.900
so they left in a hurry.

00:04:34.159 --> 00:04:35.560
So you mean...

00:04:36.159 --> 00:04:37.820
We should go back to the scene.

00:04:39.480 --> 00:04:41.210
This one should belong to a man.

00:04:41.440 --> 00:04:42.520
