00:04:59.520 --> 00:05:00.480
Like this one,

00:05:00.480 --> 00:05:01.440
a month at most.

00:05:03.960 --> 00:05:04.490
Xiaohan,

00:05:04.680 --> 00:05:05.680
take a picture of this,

00:05:05.680 --> 00:05:06.600
and search all nail salons in the city.

00:05:06.600 --> 00:05:06.930
Okay.

