Liu Jiang's clothes and ID card

00:05:09.840 --> 00:05:11.170
were all on that corpse.

00:05:11.920 --> 00:05:14.250
He was burned under Liu Jiang's identity.

00:05:15.040 --> 00:05:16.170
If Liu Jiang is dead,

00:05:17.880 --> 00:05:19.140
